  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will showcase processing a Return Repair for Rework or warranty purposes, including:</p><ul><li><p>Locating the original repair ticket</p></li><li><p>Start Return Repair</p></li><li><p>Attach the repair device</p></li><li><p>Diagnostics, estimate, logistics</p></li><li><p>Replace defective part and select supplier and RMA reason</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WwTFk4ZiTNo\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WwTFk4ZiTNo</a><h2 id=\"ProcessingaReturnRepair(video)-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1930494512/Creating+a+Quick+Sale+Ticket\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1930494512\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating a Quick Sale Ticket</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933508774/Repair+Ticket+Workflow\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933508774\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Repair Ticket Workflow</a></p>",
